  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>ElNet MC-1 counter</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p><span><span>Three-phase system for measuring energy.<br/>Up to 3 phases for energy measurement.<br/>Measurement accuracy 0.2% (0.1% on special order).<br/>1600 samples per wave.<br/>Continuous display of measurement data.<br/>Collecting energy data for 4 months.<br/>Clock with foreign exchange rates.<br/>Measuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.<br/>Support for multiple languages.<br/>RS485 communication channel.<br/>Support for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.<br/>High quality 320X240 color screen.<br/>Graphical waveform display.<br/>Simple installation on a DIN rail.<br/>TCP/IP communication, e-mail support<br/>Structured data collection.</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>Energy meters</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>Related products -</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>electrical systems</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>Control Applications Ltd</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>making contact</p>\n<p>Phone: +972-3-6474998​</p>\n<p>Fax: +972-3-6474598</p>\n<p><span>Email:<a href=\"mailto:cal@ddc.co.il\">cal@ddc.co.il</a></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>opening hours</p>\n<p>Control Applications Ltd</p>\n<p>Sunday - Thursday</p>\n<p>08:00 - 17:00</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>addr